item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - Eladio Carrion Sol Maria - [Hi-Res]
item.description:
Eladio Carrion is a successful Latin trap artist who has gained popularity for his versatility, creativity, and collaborations. He started his career as a comedian and a swimmer, but later discovered his passion for music. He has released six albums, including the recent Sol María, which he dedicated to his mother. He has also worked with some of the biggest names in the industry, such as Bad Bunny, Lil Wayne, Future, and 50 Cent. He is known for his witty lyrics, catchy hooks, and diverse influences, ranging from reggae to R&B. He has won a Latin Grammy and has charted on the Billboard 200.
